---
import { Search, LayoutList, Smile } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="py-24 sm:py-32 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-charcoal-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter"
      >
        Streamline Your Digital Life
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-800/80 dark:text-gray-300">
        Managing your subscriptions shouldn't be complicated. With SubHub, it's a simple, three-step process to bundle, save, and enjoy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 relative">
      <!-- Connecting Line -->
      <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-10 h-2/3 w-px bg-cream-300 dark:bg-charcoal-700 hidden md:block"></div>

      <div class="space-y-16 md:space-y-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div
            class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-charcoal-800 shadow-soft-light border-4 border-cream-200 dark:border-charcoal-700 mb-6"
          >
            <Search class="w-10 h-10 text-coral-500" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white">1. Discover & Choose</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-charcoal-800/70 dark:text-gray-400">Explore our extensive collection of premium services and select the ones you love.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div
            class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-charcoal-800 shadow-soft-light border-4 border-cream-200 dark:border-charcoal-700 mb-6"
          >
            <LayoutList class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-500" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white">2. Bundle & Save</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-charcoal-800/70 dark:text-gray-400">Combine your chosen subscriptions into a single, manageable bill and unlock exclusive savings.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div
            class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-charcoal-800 shadow-soft-light border-4 border-cream-200 dark:border-charcoal-700 mb-6"
          >
            <Smile class="w-10 h-10 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white">3. Manage & Enjoy</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-charcoal-800/70 dark:text-gray-400">Enjoy seamless access to all your services and manage them effortlessly from your SubHub dashboard.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
